message.body: Dont do that! You cant make me smile while im still at work! Theyll know im not focused haha!! Good morning, darling :) I love you back!
Why are you still at work?!?! And LET EM SEE YOU HAPPY! Smile smile smile. It's my favorite look on you.
Hahah you're awesome. I love you. I am smiling, trust me. And i started at 2. So no biggy
Oh. Well okay then! Oh and last night, I had a murder mystery zombie dream! Though, thinking back to it, it was probably the zombie who did it.
Ahahah darling! You crazy! Haha. Of course it was the zombie!! :)
Hahahahahaha. I love how you just nonchalantly say that it was the zombie. I feel like everyone else would be like "...what's wrong with you?!"
Hehe i know your brain...and i love it haha
Haha I love yours as well!!! Yes yes yes I do!
I got a 95 on my micro exam!!!!!! I got it was like "omg really?!" and Adam said "I do not lie!"
Wooohoooooo!!! Good job, my love!! Now quit doubting! :)
Haha. Okay. It definitely made my day! Muahahahahahah!!!!
My sister is at her jefferson interview. She said there's 4 other ppl interviewing with her!
Thats awesome, darling :) Good stuff! And...thats really weird...kinda dumb actually. Hope it goes well though!
